sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant M as Mobile App
  participant MB as Mobile BFF
  participant P as Profile Service
  participant C as Catalog Service
  participant R as Recommendations Service

  M->>MB: GET /mobile/home (JWT)
  MB->>P: GET /profile
  MB->>C: GET /featured
  MB->>R: GET /recs?limit=5
  alt Recs slow/unavailable
    MB-->>M: 200 OK (partial)\nprofile + featured (fallback recs=[])
  else Recs ok
    MB-->>M: 200 OK (mobile-shaped payload)
  end
